{"tid":2129374,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過濕疹生上頭？會唔會甩頭髮？","createTime":"2020-07-28T14:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T06:44:01.000Z","uid":2702,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"2c6cbf3f95efed8c32c1ffa70552f4fcf01dff04","tid":2129374,"uid":2702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:14:14.000Z","msg":"濕疹生到成身都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但生上個頭最辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n痕起上黎係完全忍唔住<br />\n忍20秒已經難受到全身流冷汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且勁多頭皮，返工好怕比人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家好驚甩頭髮...<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw有無人係用類固醇斷到尾？<br />\n醫生開左比我，但仲未用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b10c129649774fc814bb4d306c39684103b6c33","tid":2129374,"uid":364012,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:15:50.000Z","msg":"下世小心D啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dac93e6826f2136dd2b1569455a7fdbd970f8d1","tid":2129374,"uid":10325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食類固醇會好完一排然後又再翻發"},{"pid":"335efef7f9433508c739d1ded2f6b1b13167bce0","tid":2129374,"uid":155818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:19:39.000Z","msg":"類固醇唔會斷尾<br />\n去check下係咪食物敏感定點?"},{"pid":"52df0415c140044d5f885102b2d069cf53e3666b","tid":2129374,"uid":2702,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0dac93e6826f2136dd2b1569455a7fdbd970f8d1","tid":2129374,"uid":10325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食類固醇會好完一排然後又再翻發"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:20:31.000Z","msg":"醫生叫我用類固醇<br />\n但我上網&amp;身邊無一個人係成功用類固醇斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391fb17b0c620cccccb4f4990d72b756ac523019","tid":2129374,"uid":6057,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:25:04.000Z","msg":"上頭幾辛苦尤其出埋水<br />\n果時訓覺唔敢訓枕頭驚痴住 出街比風吹到個頭勁辛苦 要搵件風嬲笠住<br />\n我覺得起碼要用d類固醇唔比佢出水先"},{"pid":"c2415c1d7fe7ad0b685a4a29f56c2f437ca499a2","tid":2129374,"uid":62259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52df0415c140044d5f885102b2d069cf53e3666b","tid":2129374,"uid":2702,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0dac93e6826f2136dd2b1569455a7fdbd970f8d1","tid":2129374,"uid":10325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食類固醇會好完一排然後又再翻發"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:20:31.000Z","msg":"醫生叫我用類固醇<br />\n但我上網&amp;身邊無一個人係成功用類固醇斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:26:27.000Z","msg":"用少少<br />\n有時冇計"},{"pid":"c2e630e841acca050086680f2a4ca13a204199e8","tid":2129374,"uid":180825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52df0415c140044d5f885102b2d069cf53e3666b","tid":2129374,"uid":2702,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0dac93e6826f2136dd2b1569455a7fdbd970f8d1","tid":2129374,"uid":10325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食類固醇會好完一排然後又再翻發"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:20:31.000Z","msg":"醫生叫我用類固醇<br />\n但我上網&amp;身邊無一個人係成功用類固醇斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:27:37.000Z","msg":"咪撚用，我細個不停用，到高中斷尾嗰陣時真係想死咁濟"},{"pid":"aa17280e29bf1b7b985fc36be30955748084c072","tid":2129374,"uid":192993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:27:39.000Z","msg":"試下睇中醫"},{"pid":"1781de412e6b029e4330ff6a7fef37452214